data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of the sought-after Charleston Heights neighborhood! This impeccable 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom Kendrick Plan, crafted by  Schneider Custom Homes, awaits its next lucky owners. This home is move-in ready, offering you the opportunity to start creating memories from day one. No need to worry about renovations or updates – everything has been thoughtfully designed and executed to provide a seamless transition into your new home. As an added bonus the garage is equipped with an EV charging outlet.
